{"tid":2402563,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★淡出公眾視野數周後 馬雲據悉最近在海南打高爾夫","createTime":"2021-02-10T13:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T13:19:32.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5733714f22011734bb4b4c4a6ec4d89b2977abaa","tid":2402563,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:18:22.000Z","msg":"【彭博】-- 數月來，圍繞馬雲行蹤的猜測層出不窮。事實顯示，這個中國最受關注的大亨一直在練習高爾夫。<br />\n<br />\n不願具名談論非公開信息的知情人士透露，這位螞蟻集團和阿里巴巴聯合創始人近幾周在海南一座僻靜的27洞高球場--紅峽谷三亞高球會打球。這座高球場靠近海南島南端，果嶺面積廣闊風光秀麗。<br />\n<br />\n這是從1月20日馬雲與一群鄉村教師直播視頻會議以來，已知第一次被人看見。這有助於淡化人們對他可能被拘留的猜測，不過伴隨監管機構整頓其不斷擴張的商業版圖，人們對馬雲在黨內狀況的猜測還在繼續發酵。<br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴股價<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>聞訊在美股盤前交易中一度上漲1.3%。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%B7%A1%E5%87%BA%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E8%A6%96%E9%87%8E%E6%95%B8%E5%91%A8%E5%BE%8C-%E9%A6%AC%E9%9B%B2%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E6%9C%80%E8%BF%91%E5%9C%A8%E6%B5%B7%E5%8D%97%E6%89%93%E9%AB%98%E7%88%BE%E5%A4%AB-115748179.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E6%25B7%25A1%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%259C%25BE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E9%2587%258E%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25BE%258C-%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E9%259B%25B2%25E6%2593%259A%25E6%2582%2589%25E6%259C%2580%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%2588%25BE%25E5%25A4%25AB-115748179.html&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGha0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=52b22462\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%B7%A1%E5%87%BA%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E8%A6%96%E9%87%8E%E6%95%B8%E5%91%A8%E5%BE%8C-%E9%A6%AC%E9%9B%B2%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E6%9C%80%E8%BF%91%E5%9C%A8%E6%B5%B7%E5%8D%97%E6%89%93%E9%AB%98%E7%88%BE%E5%A4%AB-115748179.html</a>"},{"pid":"2cb82bd6395aa642dec2f3860f9ad37ce039b832","tid":2402563,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\"